==Turkish==
===Etymology===
From {{inh|tr|ota|یایمق|tr=yaymak|t=to spread}}, from  {{inh|tr|trk-pro|*yād-||to spread}}.<ref>{{R:tut-pro:SDM}}: [http://starling.rinet.ru/cgi-bin/response.cgi?single=1&basename=%2fdata%2falt%2faltet&text_number=2584&root=config “*ǯādV”]</ref>. Cognate with {{cog|otk||tr=yād-|t=to spread}}, {{cog|ky|жаюу||to spread}}, {{cog|uz|yoymoq||to spread}}. Compare {{cog|mn|задлах||to unleash}}.
